# `scbs`: A Command Line Tool for the Analysis of Single-Cell Bisulfite-Sequencing Data

> [!NOTE]
> This package was renamed to MethSCAn.  
> All further development will take place at its new home at [https://github.com/anders-biostat/MethSCAn](https://github.com/anders-biostat/MethSCAn).

